<div class='welcome'>
<div class='title'>Welcome</div>
<div class='text' style="font-size: 26px;">
The earliest Christians lived a faith centered around teaching,
community, service, worship, and evangelization.
In doing so, they faced imprisonment, torture, and often death.

Each age offers unique challenges to faithful.
The Christian living in our enlightened age faces challenges that are more subtle than the  &ldquo;Imperial Cult&rdquo;,
but just as deadening to the soul.

The economikon is intended to aid the modern Christian in the practice of the ancient faith,
by making information regarding these five activities easily accessible.
</div>
</div>


